items.title: Trump says China trade deal likely to be finalized during his Asia trip
items.description: President Trump told reporters as he flew into Japan that he expects to have a trade agreement with China finalized by the end of his tour of Asia.

items.title: Here's what to expect from the Fed's Wednesday interest rate meeting
